  <title>4.3.2 Removal of Cable Chain Components</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading4">拆除缆链组件</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal">确保电缆链不会妨碍将 RWH 设备安装到机床中：</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#41;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px; font-family:SimSun; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px;">松开安装螺钉和垫圈，取下电缆链盖。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal" style="margin-bottom:9px;">卸下固定缆索链固定端到缆索链固定座 [7] 的安装螺钉。</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal">卷起缆索链，并将其放在缆索链另一端的顶部，该端保持固定。</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">此外，断开夹具电源开和传感器电缆上的软管。</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:7px;"><image src="Fig 4.5 Handling of Cable Chain.png" imagestyleclass="Default" scale="70.00%" width="274" height="310" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
